  abstract={In a world full of technology, where we are accessing the files across the world that file may contain public viewable content or some more secure or private content which sometimes seems as a not eligible to view the content openly and doesn’t have rights to share it to the world due to the centralized control toward the files where it is stored. It is as a lack of confidence and integrity of the user data in current web 2.0 based storage services like big storage platform with centralized control yet gives the storage capacity of 5 to 15 gigabytes becomes an issue. This paper talk about the different protocol and advanced web resource and lots of ideas for storage issue which can be move from centralized control to the decentralized file storage platform where it doesn’t have any third-party control over the files and this can be achieved by a part of blockchain technology.},
